SR NO. 35 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend Sheriff Jason Ard and the Livingston Parish Sheriff's Office for their
outstanding achievements in combating illegal drug trafficking and protecting children
through the Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Livingston Parish Sheriff Jason Ard.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
